Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是那个电脑里面的曲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那个人就是
