Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我 其实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个 我通过电脑网络听了那只首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 特别的感动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是努力写了一首歌词
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你是否喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 难道就是 亚美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我叫西野 西野俊之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MT先生是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 通过电脑通信一直都能见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在想到底什么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起 不 太高兴了就
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是您的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很久以前就听她提起你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他说了我们什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误会啊 我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方站着太不礼貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如到我工作的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们走吧
