Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的梦想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是作曲家还是钢琴家
